Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.190 --> 00:00:05.088
You're already familiar with what may
well be the key tool for patients,

00:00:05.088 --> 00:00:07.616
the personal health record, or PHR.

00:00:07.616 --> 00:00:11.517
While the exact form of a PHR is
evolving, the central ideas for

00:00:11.517 --> 00:00:14.754
a long time have been that
it is patient controlled,

00:00:14.754 --> 00:00:20.670
patient's record data that could become
part of their electronic health record.

00:00:20.670 --> 00:00:25.980
Patients control access to their data,
and it's a life long record.

